# Environment Variables Template — OprexDuit

Copy file ini ke `.env.local` (frontend) atau `.env` (backend) dan isi nilainya.
File `.env.local` sudah ada di .gitignore — aman.

---

## Frontend (.env.local)

```env
# Backend API URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# Supabase (wajib — ambil dari Supabase dashboard → Settings → API)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://<project-id>.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...
```

## Backend (.env) — juga set di Render dashboard sebagai env vars

```env
# CORS — set ke URL Vercel production
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://oprexduit.vercel.app,http://localhost:3000

# Supabase (wajib — ambil dari Supabase dashboard → Settings → API)
SUPABASE_URL=https://<project-id>.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key   # JANGAN commit ke git
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret              # Settings → API → JWT Secret

# AI Provider (Phase AI)
AI_PROVIDER=deepseek
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your-deepseek-key
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key

# Payment (Phase 6)
MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY=your-midtrans-key
MIDTRANS_CLIENT_KEY=your-midtrans-client-key
MIDTRANS_IS_PRODUCTION=false
```

> Lihat SECRETS.md (lokal, tidak di-commit) untuk nilai production lengkap.
